data.description: Price improvement!!!! This beautiful, cozy home is located in a great community near the airport and minutes from downtown. If you love hiking, biking, swimming, fishing, or camping, the home is near Mckinney Falls State Park.  You will enjoy walks to the nearby community center and large park & pool. Living here makes it an easy trip to the airport; you will be near schools, shopping, restaurants, and much more. Save on your energy bill with this home's solar panels. This one can be your home. Please get in touch with me for more information or to schedule a showing.
